ex broadly black and base narrowly black extending medially to disc. Pygidium length:width ratio 1:1.5, angulate in lateral view, with a narrow, arcuate, slightly obtuse angle post midlength; surface concentrically rugulose with centre post midlength bearing sparse, short, pale setae at apex and basolateral angles. Genitalia (
